Prepare spaghetti according to package directions; drain. In medium skillet, heat oil. Add Hillshire Farm Smoked Sausage and remaining ingredients, except spaghetti. Stir-fry until sausage is browned and vegetables are tender. Add spaghetti; toss to coat. Heat through. Arrange on warm serving platter. Garnish as desired. Serve immediately. Refrigerate leftovers.